Borg
The Borg (Full Conversion Cyborg) has replaced most of their biological body
with a powerful mechanical chassis. What remains is a human mind encased in
Mega-Damage armour with built-in weapons and superhuman strength.

Borgs are among the toughest characters in the game. They cannot be Juiced or
take most bionic additions (no room), and they require maintenance instead of
food. Their advancement is slower than most OCCs to reflect their inherent power.

Attribute requirements: PS 14, PE 12.
Flags: [Full Conversion Borg] [Cybernetic]
Starting equipment: Full conversion cyborg body (military or civilian chassis),
two integrated ranged weapons, vibro-blade, and maintenance toolkit.
